---
// src/pages/index.astro

/**
 * Home Page
 * This is the main landing page of the website.
 */

import IndexPageLayout from '../layouts/IndexPageLayout.astro';
import Lang from '../components/Lang.astro';
import QuoteBlock from '../components/QuoteBlock.astro';
import TableOfContents from '../components/TableOfContents.astro';

import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

// define the metadata for the page, including title and description in both languages
// { pageTitle } and { pageDesc } are passed as props to PageLayout,
// which will use them in the <head> for SEO and display
// and further support language toggle
const pageTitle = "Homepage"
const pageDesc = {
    zh: '我在这个网站上分享我在生活和技术方面的所思所想',
    en: 'This site is where I share my thoughts and research on technology, healthcare, and life.',
};
const intro = {
    zh: 'Hi，我是文康丞，一个在医学院苦苦挣扎的医学生',
    en: 'I\'m Kangcheng Wen, a medical student struggling in med school. ',
}
---

<IndexPageLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDesc} intro={intro}>

    <h2>
        <Lang is="zh">页面导览</Lang>
        <Lang is="en">NAVIGATION</Lang>
    </h2>

    <p>
        <Lang is="zh">
            这里有不定期掉落技术干货的<a href="/blogs">博客</a>；
            <a href="/lab">微研究</a>板块记录着我源于生活脑洞的小调查或研究；
            <a href="/thoughts">随想</a>则是一些不成体系的碎片化思考，也包含了一些牢骚；
            <a href="/aboutMe">关于我</a>和<a href="/aboutWebsite">关于这个网站</a>提供了更多的背景信息。
            你可以通过顶部的导航栏访问不同部分。
        </Lang>
        <Lang is="en">
            Pop into my <a href="/blogs">Blogs</a> for occasional tech posts,
            or check out the <a href="/lab">Mini Lab</a> for survey or research inspired by daily life.
            <a href="/thoughts">Thoughts</a> is a collection of fragmented musings (and the occasional rant).
            For the full backstory, visit <a href="/aboutMe">About Me</a> and <a href="/aboutWebsite">About This Site</a>.
            You can access different sections through the navigation bar at the top.
        </Lang>
    </p>

    <h2>
        <Lang is="zh">此时此刻</Lang>
        <Lang is="en">Now</Lang>
    </h2>

    <p>
        <Lang is="zh">
            目前就读于<a href="https://www.pku.edu.cn/">北京大学</a>-
            <a href="https://sbms.bjmu.edu.cn/">基础医学院</a>（医专） 临床医学专业
            （如果你对此感兴趣，建议直接问 AI，毕竟医学部官网常年“抽风”，不过我几乎不推荐任何人感兴趣...）。
            平时常驻北京海淀，假期回家乡云南躺平。
            现混迹于<a href="https://www.puh3.net.cn/">北医三院</a>某课题组，试图搞懂 AI 在医疗领域的应用。
            虽然对 AI 充满热情，但感觉离真正的“科研”还有亿点距离；基础医学院的课业也让我头秃，经常学得云里雾里。
            结果就是——我在两边都是个略显笨拙的“门外汉”。
            我也许（并不）能帮你看看膝关节的问题。
            搭建这个网站是为了记录学习、分享想法，欢迎随时找我聊天。
            更多信息请移步<a href="/aboutMe">关于我</a>。
        </Lang>
        <Lang is="en">
            I'm currently surviving medical school at <a href="https://www.pku.edu.cn">Peking University</a>-<a href="https://sbms.bjmu.edu.cn/">School of Basic Medical Sciences</a>.
            I'm based in Haidian, Beijing, though I escape to my hometown in Yunnan whenever possible.
            I'm interning at a research group in <a href="https://www.puh3.net.cn/">Peking University Third Hospital</a>, exploring AI in healthcare.
            I'm fascinated by AI algorithms, even if "real research" feels lightyears away. Meanwhile, medical school is... humbling (read: I'm struggling to get decent scores).
            So, I'm basically a "Level 2 Dabbler" in both fields.
            I might (read: definitely shouldn't) offer advice on your knees.
            This site is where I document my learning curve and random thoughts. I'm always open to a chat!
            More info can be found on the <a href="/aboutMe">About Me</a> page.
        </Lang>
    </p>

    <p>
        <Lang is="zh">
            开发和部署这个网站的目的是想让我慢慢跻身入“深度思考者”的行列。
            在浑浑噩噩摆摆烂烂度过我的大二上学期后，我意识到自己需要一个平台来记录和分享我的思考过程，迫使自己去深入思考一些问题，而不是停留在表面。
            我非常认可<code>费曼学习法</code>
            （这篇<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/118183282">知乎文章</a>对此有很好的介绍，
            我很喜欢的博主<a href="https://space.bilibili.com/391930545">Maki</a>有一系列视频详细完整地讲解费曼学习法的实践），
            而我希望这个网站就是我实践费曼学习法的产物之一。
            这个网站就是我为自己设立的输出平台，虽然现在内容还很稀少，但我会持续更新博客和随想，并偶尔发布一些微研究的成果。
            我还有更多开发这个网站的动机，更多信息包括网站搭建的过程、网站的设计等可以在<a href="/aboutWebsite">关于这个网站</a>页面找到。
        </Lang>
        <Lang is="en">
            I built this website to pull myself out of a sophomore slump and force myself into "Deep Thinker" mode.
            After spending my sophomore fall in a haze of procrastination,
            I realized I needed a platform to document my thought process and stop skimming the surface of knowledge.
            I'm a big fan of the <code>Feynman Technique</code>
            (this <a href="https://fs.blog/feynman-technique/">article</a> gives a good introduction to it, you can google it yourself or chat with GPTs if you don't know it),
            and I hope this website is one of the products of my practice of the Feynman Technique.
            This website is the platform I set up for myself, and although the content is still sparse,
            It's quite empty right now, but I promise to keep updating my blogs, thoughts, and the occasional mini-research project.
            For the tech stack and the overly complex backstory of why I built this, check out <a href="/aboutWebsite">About This Site</a>.
        </Lang>
    </p>

    <h2>
        <Lang is="zh">联系我</Lang>
        <Lang is="en">Connect</Lang>
    </h2>

    <p>
        <Lang is="zh">
            欢迎通过邮件联系我：<a href="mailto:kangchengwen@proton.me">kangchengwen@proton.me</a> 或 <a href="mailto:syncrexwen@stu.pku.edu.cn">syncrexwen@stu.pku.edu.cn</a>
        </Lang>
        <Lang is="en">
            Reach me at <a href="mailto:kangchengwen@proton.me">kangchengwen@proton.me</a> or <a href="mailto:syncrexwen@stu.pku.edu.cn">syncrexwen@stu.pku.edu.cn</a>
        </Lang>
    </p>

    <Lang is="zh">
        <QuoteBlock cite="胡适">怕什么真理无穷，进一寸有一寸的欢喜。</QuoteBlock>
    </Lang>
    <Lang is="en">
        <QuoteBlock cite="Samuel Beckett">Ever tried. Ever failed. No matter. Try again. Fail again. Fail better. </QuoteBlock>
    </Lang>

</IndexPageLayout>
